{
  "stem": "24466.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] That they were shot there, singly, and he was buried them, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] nine people after a paper with bitumen-- bitumen paper or something like that, and after another paper, and buried them there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I asked him, could you show me that place?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took a carriage, a [NON-ENGLISH], they called this, and I went over there with him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's showing me the place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I noticed-- so I start to do some-- I was trying to do the exhumation, and to-- but where?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know where the-- what to do, you know, or to exhumate, but where to bury?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- I came the second time there to find out if-- because I notice that it's flat, you know, because there are some other graves from Russian P-- [INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Prisoners of war, prisoners of war, 32 in every-- in every grave was, and that was still-- how you are calling this?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A little--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mound.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A mound of earth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here that was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the owner from that part came to me and tell me, listen, you haven't got what to look after here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You can see, and he mentioned that to me, that a month ago, two months ago, I don't remember what he said, but a short time ago, before the Radom was liberated through the Russian army, a Sondercommando from Jews under the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and on top, who was carrying them on?",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That will come to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mendelsson. ?] A chap, he was--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
